\begin_layout Standard
Why do correlations so strongly diverge in negatively autocorrelated environment
s (Figure 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "fig:correlation"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

